{
  "stem": "21919.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As it turned out, this was probably a very safe place for them to be, because nobody would think that they were there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She took me one day when he wasn't there and asked them to come out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said to them that-- that I'm working for her now and told them to-- she repeated in front of them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She says, I told her that if she's going to mention to anybody that you're staying here, that you're going to kill her.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have nothing to lose, right?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because either way, you're going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you'll make sure that she goes with you, right?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said, right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was very surprised.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was very confused.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know if I should tell them who I am, so they wouldn't be scared of me, or I heard stories at church all the time that when they said, once you catch a Jew, he tells you about the other Jews.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by now, there are none, because once you punish them, they tell you where other Jews are.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They know where they are.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I took this into consideration, that if you punish somebody, maybe they'll give it out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it wasn't fair for them to treat me different.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If they knew I was Jewish, maybe they'll be more familiar, and then she'll find out that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was something I was not sleeping over quite a few nights, thinking what was the right thing to do.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I decided, for everybody's protection, I'm not going to tell them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they called me like, young lady.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In German, they say fraulein, or in Polish, panienka.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't call me by my name at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What name were you using?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
